{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>1. MOVE</strong></h2>Your score is the distance you reach. Distance controls everything. Keep moving forward to unlock guns, to regen, to find loot.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016900/extras/move.gif?t=1723495848\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>2. KILL</strong></h2>The further you go, the harder it gets. Get ready to kill your way through swarms of enemies.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016900/extras/fight.gif?t=1723495848\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>3. UPGRADE</strong></h2>Get the biggest guns you can find. Stack as many passive perks as you can. But don't kill yourself with your new toys.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016900/extras/upgrade.gif?t=1723495848\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>4. GET CREATIVE</strong></h2>Skills won't be enough to survive, you\u2019ll have to get creative to go further. Use the environment. Exploit the physics.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016900/extras/creative.gif?t=1723495848\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>ABOUT</strong></h2>I'm Aurelien Rodot, a freelance engineer. Scree is a pet project I\u2019m doing for fun, I hope you\u2019ll have fun too :)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEEDBACK</strong></h2>Feedback really helps me, please post what you like and what you don't in the steam community or on our discord server.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2016900?t=1723495848","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016900/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1723495848","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016900/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1723495848","capsule_imagev5":"https://sh